Consts.useLimit: Map titles, notes, and footnotes should correspond with supplemental information provided in separate XLS spreadsheet for CHS year. Map variables are reported with one decimal. Zeros represent null values and should be interpreted as null values. Varialbes flagged as unreliable (i.e. Aircon2_r = 1) should be marked / hatched on the map as unreliable. Variables flagged as suppressed (i.e. Aircon2_s = 1) should appear as having no data (i.e. blank areas) on the map.
